      • repeat_WS_VAL

        public java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.Integer> repeat_WS_VAL(long i)
        Compare Vali_i with each Vali_j and j < i, if for any j, the predecessor that decides Val repeats, stop. Return the repeated WS_VAL(s), with last element of Alpha_1, i.e. j, when for the first time this WS_VAL_i = WS_VAL_j;
